name: Brownie Points
description:
Brownie Points!

Remove the letters of "Brownie" to change the character/characters actions to complete the puzzle!

I forgot to add borders so watch out for the edges or use the respawn button.

Sorry for no sound 

Made in 2 hours and 58 mins! 

Made in Godot

Hints Below

1st level: What does a dog normally like?

2nd level: What do you use to shoot a target?

3rd level: How do you move a boat?

4th level: What's missing from the trophy?
